Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她送我禮物後 要我以三倍回報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欠款變成三倍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進藤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明送的是狗糧 太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進藤 鎌倉在聽著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她簡直是惡鬼啊 惡鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要再折磨自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就8000元啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9000元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就認了吧 宮越
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己挖的坑要自己填上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出那巧克力的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造成東那樣子的人也是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1000元就算了 你就大方一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9000元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我什麼都沒有收到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現金就行了 三倍回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就什麼都沒有 乘以三倍也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3乘以0等於3萬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妃你也是 不要再敲詐店長了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟他有錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你那麼有錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然你在這群怪人中並不顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在仔細想想會覺得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭到宮越的暴力也不會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好失禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被妃敲詐也不痛不癢她給錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好失禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明這麼沒用卻是店長
